Class MyStack<T>

java.lang.Object
MyStack<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the stack
All Implemented Interfaces:
StackADT<T>
public class MyStack<T> extends Object implements StackADT<T>
Generic LIFO (last-in-first-out) stack class. Maximum number of elements allowed is 1000 and a default size of 10 if the size is not declared.
